UConstable Vuyani Brian Welcome (28) uvume icala lokubulala owayeyintombi yakhe uConstable Ayanda Zanele Sibiya (29) eNkantolo eNkulu eMgungundlovu ngoMsombuluko. UConstable Sibiya watholwa ebulewe emotweni yakhe ngo- Agasti 19 ngowedlule, wayehlezi esihlalweni somgibeli enenxeba lokudutshulwa. Encwadini esenkantolo, avume icala. Uthe wayenezintombi ezimbili, umufi nenye. Uthe umufi wakhulelwa kodwa saphuphuma isisu. Enye intombi nayo kuthiwa yatshela umbulali ukuthi izithwele. Umufi wezwa ngokukhulelwa kwenye intombi lapho kwaqala khona ingxabano phakathi kwephoyisa nomufi. Umbulali uthe watshela umufi ukuthi abahlukane. Ngelanga ambulala ngalo,  umbulali uthe wayefuna izinto zakhe zokugqoka ezazikumufi, bahlela ukuba bahlangane edolobheni. Evuma icala uthe umufi wayelokhu emthethisa ethi sekungaze kuphele ngothando lwabo ngenxa yokukhulelwa kwenye intombi yakhe. Umbulali uthe wanengeka wagcina edubule umufi. Uthe wabe esembeka esihlalweni somgibeli, wathatha imoto wayoyishiya eceleni komgwaqo. Yena wacela ukugitsheliswa ngezinye izimoto, waya kubo wafika walala. Isidumbu sikamufi satholwa emotweni, wabe eseboshwa emuva kwezinsuku ezimbalwa sitholiwe. Kulindeleke ukuba abezenhlalakahle balethe umbiko ngombulali, bese nabaphenyi behlanganisa izitatimende zabathintekayo ecaleni. Umbulali uyobe esegwetshwa khona eNkantolo eNkulu. Umufi washiya izingane zakhe ezimbili. Umbulali unengane encane esanda kubelethwa yintombi yakhe.